Document: BoneMap
Path: godot/classes/class_bonemap.rst
Summary: Methods for mapping skeleton and profile bone names during retargeting processes.

Method: find_profile_bone_name(skeleton_bone_name: StringName) → StringName
Returns a profile bone name associated with the given skeleton bone name. If no mapping exists, returns empty StringName. Note: In the retargeting process, the returned bone name corresponds to the target skeleton's bone structure.

Method: get_skeleton_bone_name(profile_bone_name: StringName) → StringName
Returns the skeleton bone name mapped to the specified profile bone name. Note: In the retargeting process, the returned bone name corresponds to the source skeleton's bone structure.

Method: set_skeleton_bone_name(profile_bone_name: StringName, skeleton_bone_name: StringName)
Maps the specified skeleton bone name to the given profile bone name. Note: In the retargeting process, the setting bone name corresponds to the source skeleton's bone structure.